data.text:
Michael Caine (b. March 14, 1933) is a British character actor who portrayed Alfred Pennyworth in the Dark Knight Trilogy, and voiced him in the tie-in video game Batman Begins.

Pictured: Caine as Alfred Pennyworth from Batman Begins
